---++ 2018-05-23
---++++ meeting notes
   * Format for Inception
      * One file per argument including the following two lines
         * stance + topic, e.g. "PRO nuclear energy"
         * sentence, e.g. "Nuclear energy is safe and cheap ."
      * File name: !RandomNumber_Stance_Topic_SentencesHash, e.g. 005_pro_nuclear-energy_5345354jhhj453g543.txt
      * Files should be randomized to prevent bias
   * Next steps
      * Finish data cleaning, and create data statistics
      * Prepare files for inception and integrate them in the system
      * Elaborate guideline, i.e. add "simplification"

